{"tid":682022,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【嘲利物浦門將】小米抽錯火水　辣㷫球迷刪帖　小米香港：傷害球迷感情感抱歉","createTime":"2018-05-28T13:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T15:49:23.000Z","uid":188606,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a934bb4f328672ed68bec67b857b0b069ab4ab6e","tid":682022,"uid":188606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180528/large/1527496932_02c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180528%2Flarge%2F1527496932_02c8.jpg&h=8e24e3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2080000/2082271/2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2080000%2F2082271%2F2_600.jpg&h=ac922d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/mi-09_4gHkr_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmi-09_4gHkr_1200x0.png&h=e22b740a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利物浦門將卡利奧斯於歐聯決賽兩度犯錯，連累球隊失冠。「小米香港」今日在FB發文「抽水」，豈料卻「抽錯火水」辣㷫一眾球迷。小米隨即刪帖，並為傷害球迷感情而表示抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n「小米香港」今日在FB專頁，借卡利奧斯的失誤推銷自家品牌的行李箱。帖文以「你走喇！我唔想搞大佢」為題，指紅軍球迷應該送行李箱給卡利奧斯，讓他盡快離隊，還hashtag「#堅固過龍門」及「#Youwillneverwalkalone」作嘲諷。<br />\n<br />\n帖文一出，「小米香港」即被大批球迷圍攻。小米隨即刪帖，但仍然有不少網民「cap圖」留底，並在小米FB留言要求小米回應。「小米香港」的小編則對事件表示抱歉，「 今次因為小編嘅輕率而傷害咗球迷嘅感情，對此感到非常抱歉，小米一直非常重視大家嘅支持，無意傷害任何人嘅感情，日後亦會更謹慎及小心，希望各位米粉和球迷可以繼續支持小米」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/1691357664283180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F1691357664283180&d=a%2FgG8cP4M3Rftnet3o2OSozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=df906845\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/1691357664283180</a>"},{"pid":"34313d5ece767eca621109aad641